yauvanayuktām mām upekṣya niṣphalaṃ śūnyatāyāṃ dṛṣṭiḥ | ayam abhiprāyaḥ | śūnyatākaruṇābhinnaṃ hi mahāsukhajñānaṃ nirmāṇasaṃbhogakāyadvayavyatirekeṇopalabhyate | nirmāṇasaṃbhogakāyau tu bhujamukhasaṃsthānamayau strīpuruṣarūpau tau ca bhāvanālabhyau | bhāvanā ca yuvativyatirekeṇa na bhavati | anyathā vikṣiptacittatvād iti yata evaṃ tasmāc chūnyasvabhāvaṃ viśeṣeṇa garhitvā nindatvā kuru tvaṃ mayā sārdhaṃ ghṛṣṭim āliṅganacumbanādikam ity arthaḥ |
